name: LOUIS VUITTON EXOTIQUE GLOBAL PREMIER IN SINGAPORE
description: Louis Vuitton – Exotics Collection. A world premiere in Singapore. Interior Design by Baroness Rose Anne de Pampelonne. Scope of Work: Venue sourcing, spatial planning, layout, restoration of house, liaison with interior designer, fabrication and build of fittings, aircon and electrical fittings, landscaping and pest control, full on-site event management.

name: LOUIS VUITTON EXOTIQUE GLOBAL PREMIER IN SINGAPORE
description: A Cruise 20 Press Presentation and Cocktail Event for media professionals held in Singapore. Scope of Work: Design adaption from global guidelines, spatial planning, fabrication and build, furniture sourcing, guests & hospitality management.
